  "description": "<ul><li>Own UHNW/HNW client acquisition and retention; build and manage key accounts.</li><li>Work closely with other global heads for strategy and optimization of total company resources.</li><li>Oversee end-to-end design of complex, multi-country luxury itineraries </li><li>Enhance partner relations (hotels, DMCs, airlines), service standards, and develop a regional client service team </li></ul><p><br /><br /></p><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Atleast 10 years of Luxury Travel management experience</li><li>Proven new-business acquisition and relationship development</li><li>Immediate starter is preferred</li><li></li></ul><p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>strader@talenttradersg.com</strong></p><p><br /><br /></p><p>EA License No.: 13C6305<br /></p><p>Registration No.: R23117344(TIONG TIAN HO)</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
